'''Task Force Aleph''' was an element of the [[New Republic Fifth Fleet]] that attempted to jump from [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]] to [[Fondor/Legends|Fondor]] to reinforce the [[New Republic First Fleet|First Fleet]] during the [[Battle of Fondor]]. Half the force was yanked from [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] by [[dovin basal]] mines, and six ships were pulled into [[Mass shadow/Legends|mass shadows]]. The fleet was forced to retreat before ever reaching [[Fondor/Legends|Fondor]]. The planet would eventually fall.

